==Reputation== Ivy League medical schools have some of the best reputations among medical schools in the United States.{{citation needed|date=September 2018}} They are some of the oldest institutions of medical education, and leaders among medical research. They are also associated with some of the best [[hospitals]] in the United States. Some publications' most recent rankings of medical schools at these institutions are shown below.
